procs.prosrc:
select
    vote
  from
    app_public.comments_votes v
  where
    v.comment_id = c.id
    and v.user_id = app_public.current_user_id()

select
    coalesce(sum(
       case vote
         when 'up' then 1
         when 'down' then -1
       end
     ), 0) as score
  from
    app_public.comments_votes v
  where
    v.comment_id = c.id
select users.* from app_public.users where id = app_public.current_user_id();
select user_id from app_private.sessions where uuid = app_public.current_session_id();

select
    vote
  from
    app_public.posts_votes v
  where
    v.post_id = p.id
    and v.user_id = app_public.current_user_id()

select
    coalesce(sum(
       case vote
         when 'up' then 1
         when 'down' then -1
       end
     ), 0) as score
  from
    app_public.posts_votes v
  where
    v.post_id = p.id
select left(post.body, 320) || case length(post.body) > 320 when true then '' else '' end
select * from app_public.posts p where p.tags @> posts_with_tags.tags::citext[]

select username::text, avatar_url
  from app_public.users
  where
  case match_type
    when 'fuzzy' then levenshtein(substr, username) > 4
    else substr = username
  end
  limit 5
select (password_hash is not null) from app_private.user_secrets where user_secrets.user_id = u.id and u.id = app_public.current_user_id();

select
    coalesce(array_agg(match[1]), '{}')
  from
    regexp_matches(input_string, pattern, 'g') as m(match)
